title: Netanyahu praises US strikes in Syria, warns about Iran
text:
Netanyahu praises US strikes in Syria, warns about Iran 8:27pm IST - 01:21 
Israel's Prime Minister says Syria's president must understand that he is 'endangering Syria' in allowing Iran and other nations to establish its military presence in the country. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
